{"_id":"MTEzNTc0MTRlMWI5","name":"Tangled Web","permission":{"default":2},"folder":"MDU0YWU4MzFmMTE1","sort":150000,"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":15,"handout-archived":false}},"content":"<h1>Tangled Web</h1><p>Secret temples exist in great numbers in Undermountain, particularly those of evil gods not welcomed in the city above. The vile servants of these deities are locked in an endless war for supremacy in the dark dungeon. Lolth, the Demon Queen of Spiders, is the fiendish mastermind behind many of these bloody conflicts.</p><div><br></div>","img":"assets/art/shared_worlds/journal/032_-_Secrets_Deck_Handouts/015_-_Tangled_Web/avatar.png"}
