{"_id":"N2ExNDAzZTk3ZTli","name":"Pot of Awakening","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZDVkNGI3NGVkMTk0","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":55,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":550000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Pot of Awakening</h4><p><i>Wondrous item, common</i><br></p><p>If one plants an ordinary shrub in the pot and lets it grow for 30 days, the shrub magically transforms into an <a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Actor data-id=YjMwZmQwYjQ4YjVh ><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>awakened shrub</a> at the end of that time. When the shrub awakens, its roots break the pot, destroying it. The awakened shrub is friendly toward whoever planted it. Absent commands from its creator, it does nothing.<br></p>\n<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><br></section>","img":""}
