{"_id":"NDc3ZTc3ZjM3NGIx","name":"Mariner's Armor (Scale Mail)","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZDVkNGI3NGVkMTk0","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":45,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":450000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<p><h4>Mariner's Armor (Scale Mail)</h4><i>Armor (medium), uncommon</i></p><p>While wearing this armor, you have a swimming speed equal to your walking speed. In addition, whenever you start your turn underwater with 0 hit points,&nbsp; the armor causes you to rise 60 feet toward the surface. The armor is decorated with fish and shell motifs.</p>","img":""}
