{"_id":"Nzg1ZjBkZWRmYTc0","name":"Level 1: Dungeon Level","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MTAxYmVmOTNlNWY5","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":0,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":0,"entryTime":0,"content":"\n<section class=\"secret\"><p>GM Notes : </p><h2>Level 1: Dungeon Level</h2>The Dungeon Level is designed for four 5th-level characters, and characters who defeat the monsters on this level should gain enough XP to reach 6th level.<br></section>","img":"assets/art/shared_worlds/journal/002_-_Level_1_3A_Dungeon_Level/000_-_Level_1_3A_Dungeon_Level/avatar.png"}
{"_id":"Nzk3NTcwZDJlZDc4","name":"Potion of Gaseous Form","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MzEwZWQwN2I5NTYw","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":8,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":80000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<p></p><h4>Potion of Gaseous Form</h4><i>Potion, rare</i><p></p><p>When you drink this potion, you gain the effect of the <i><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Item data-id=YzlhNmVlNmFjN2Fh ><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i>gaseous form</a></i> spell for 1 hour (no concentration required) or until you end the effect as a bonus action. This potion's container seems to hold fog that moves and pours like water.<br></p>","img":""}
{"_id":"Nzk5ZTU4Mzc5ZGQw","name":"Candle of the Deep","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZDVkNGI3NGVkMTk0","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":11,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":110000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<p><h4>Candle of the Deep</h4><i>Wondrous item, common</i></p><p>The flame of the <i>candle of the deep</i>&nbsp;is not extinguished when immersed in water. It gives off light and heat like a normal candle.</p>","img":""}
