{"_id":"OTkzYmRjODYxYWZk","name":"Nester's Fate","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MDU0YWU4MzFmMTE1","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":5,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":50000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h1>Nester’s Fate</h1><p>Halaster brought seven apprentices with him to Undermountain. One of them, Nester, became a lich using spells and methods of his own devising. But his process was flawed, and over time Nester’s phylactery and body disintegrated until only his floating skull and skeletal arms remained. Driven mad by his failure to achieve true lichdom, Nester continues to haunt Undermountain in this weakened form.</p><div><br></div>","img":"assets/art/shared_worlds/journal/032_-_Secrets_Deck_Handouts/005_-_Nester_27s_Fate/avatar.png"}
