{"_id":"ZGEzZTUzOGQzZDVk","name":"Quaal's Feather Token (Tree)","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"ZDVkNGI3NGVkMTk0","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":60,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":600000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Quaal's Feather Token (Tree)</h4><p><i>Wondrous item, rare</i></p><p>This tiny object looks like a feather. You must be outdoors to use this token. You can use an action to touch it on an unoccupied space on the ground. The token disappears, and in its place a nonmagical oak tree springs into existence. The tree is 60 feet tall and has a 5-foot-diameter trunk, and its branches at the top spread out in a 20-foot-radius.<br></p>","img":"assets/art/shared_worlds/journal/029_-_Magic_Items/060_-_Quaal_27s_Feather_Token__28Tree_29/avatar_1.png"}
