{"_id":"ZWE3ZjEzZWE0OWNl","name":"Potion of Diminution","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MzEwZWQwN2I5NTYw","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":4,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":40000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Potion of Diminution</h4><p><i>Potion, rare</i><br></p><p>When you drink this potion, you gain the \"reduce\" effect of the <i><a class=\"entity-link\" data-entity=Item data-id=ZjVlOGQyN2QyNmQx ><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i>enlarge/reduce</a></i> spell for 1d4 hours (no concentration required). The red in the potion's liquid continuously contracts to a tiny bead and then expands to color the clear liquid around it. Shaking the bottle fails to interrupt this process.<br></p>","img":""}
